<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Daily Check - {{userName}}</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { text-align: center; background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        .question { background: #fff3cd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; }
        .buttons { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px; }
        .btn-success { background: #28a745; color: white; }
        .btn-danger { background: #dc3545; color: white; }
        .details { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #6c757d; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Daily Check for {{userName}}</h1>
        <p>Date: {{checkDate}}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="question">
        <h2>Did {{userName}} drink alcohol yesterday?</h2>
        <p>Please click one of the buttons below to record your response.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="buttons">
        <a href="{{baseUrl}}/trustman/response/{{token}}?response=clean" class="btn btn-success">
            No, they stayed clean ✓
        </a>
        <a href="{{baseUrl}}/trustman/response/{{token}}?response=drank" class="btn btn-danger">
            Yes, they drank alcohol ✗
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="details">
        <p><strong>Bet Details:</strong></p>
        <p>Amount: ${{amount}}</p>
        <p>Deadline: {{deadline}}</p>
        <p>Your response helps determine if {{userName}} succeeds in their commitment.</p>
        <p>This link expires in 24 hours.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>